\q1 m…ôto t…ôtawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm net…ômim koatos-i…ôhau r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Prov 3:34; 1 Pita 5:5\x*
