\p 
\v 11 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. Sot…ôghat rat…ôn e n…ôrg…®t…ômat m…®n. Ok…ôm…ô suah kit tat…ôghat rat e n…ôrg…® pian kit, o in tat…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn kit m…ôm…ô in t…ômol t…ôfag…ô rat kit,\f + \fr 4:11 \ft N…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha Jemes n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôs…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat ok…ôsot…ôg…ôtun…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôha net…ômim. N…ôghat…ôn m…®n tep…ôt e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôk…ôike mot…ôg…ôtun t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôha et…ômim m…ôm…ô in otiet r…ôk…®s lan. M…ôto kot…ôk…ôike motol e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn it…ôm t…ôtat…®g …ôl…ôhau. Kal 6:1; Luk 17:3; 2 Tim 3:16; Jem 5:20; Kal 5:21; 1 Tes 5:14; 2 Tes 3:15; Taet 3:10.\f* k…ôn suah …ôh, in tat…ôghat rat e lou\f + \fr 4:11 \ft ‚ÄúLou‚Äù e ves u tat…ôghat-in ‚Äòlou r…ôha nolkeike…ôn.‚Äô ∆èplan-tu Jem 2:8\f* mat…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô lou t…ôsahmen…ôn m…ôm…ô in otol r…ôhan w…ôk, o k…ôm-naka lou in nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm. K…ôn nian nakoat…ôplan lou m…ôm…ô in t…ôsahmen…ôn, it…ômat n…ôk…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn lou, m…ôto n…ômot…ôr k…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr e lou, k…ôn m…ôsotat…®g ahgin…ôn lou.
\v 12 Uhg…®n …ôm in tatos-ipa Lou, k…ôn in …ôm t…ôtakil net…ômim mat…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn lan. K…ôn in t…®tun nosmeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn m…®tun n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn. ?M…ôto it…ômat, n…®kit…ômat t…ôht m…ôm…ô it…ômat Uhg…®n m…®n, m…ôm…ô nakotakil t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n r…ôha piat…ômat m…®n motu…ôh ilat? !K…ôp!\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Rom 2:1; 14:4 \x*
\s1 N…ôghat…ôn ausit
